%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Talk_Stage09_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: fed8a0e3774e16444a047179eaa30d40, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 168713220096
    m_Localized: Well hello, Mr. Mouse.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168755163136
    m_Localized: What are you doing in a place like this?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168755163137
    m_Localized: I was looking at this painting.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357440
    m_Localized: It is a painting of a little dog who set off a bomb.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357441
    m_Localized: I can see that!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357442
    m_Localized: It happens often here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357443
    m_Localized: Someone activates a bomb without looking ahead.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357444
    m_Localized: One small mistake can leave you badly hurt.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357445
    m_Localized: This place is dangerous.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357446
    m_Localized: That is why most people
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357447
    m_Localized: settle down in the safe sections, right?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357448
    m_Localized: Yes. Most of us stay in the safe sections,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357449
    m_Localized: and live quietly without making waves.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357450
    m_Localized: Surely you are the same.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357451
    m_Localized: Not a chance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357452
    m_Localized: I am not spending my whole life in a terrarium.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357453
    m_Localized: I am getting outside.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357454
    m_Localized: ...Outside?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357455
    m_Localized: (Damn it. That was the forbidden word.)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357456
    m_Localized: I used to be outside too, just like you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357457
    m_Localized: ?! You did?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357458
    m_Localized: Yes. But
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357459
    m_Localized: it is not a place of hope.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357460
    m_Localized: I will never forget it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357461
    m_Localized: I was inside a cold metal cage.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357462
    m_Localized: Huge eyes peered in at me.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357463
    m_Localized: And strange-colored food
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357464
    m_Localized: was forced down my throat again and again,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357465
    m_Localized: until one day I found myself dropped into this world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357466
    m_Localized: It was a very long time ago,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357467
    m_Localized: but that fear is still soaked into my bones.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357468
    m_Localized: For you, outside
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357469
    m_Localized: may be somewhere to return to.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357470
    m_Localized: But for me,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357471
    m_Localized: it is somewhere I never want to go back to.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357472
    m_Localized: Yes! I went through the exact same thing!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357473
    m_Localized: What?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357474
    m_Localized: I see. Then you and I share the same circumstances.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357475
    m_Localized: I only remember my time in that cage as a blur.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357476
    m_Localized: Not because it was long ago.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357477
    m_Localized: I was in a haze the entire time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357478
    m_Localized: Only the sensations remain.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357479
    m_Localized: I want to know how to get out.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357480
    m_Localized: How to get out?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357481
    m_Localized: Even if we went through the same thing,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357482
    m_Localized: I cannot share that desire.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357483
    m_Localized: I am sorry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357484
    m_Localized: I cannot help you with that.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357485
    m_Localized: However, I do find this suspicious.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357486
    m_Localized: This world has several strange rules.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357487
    m_Localized: Not only the rules needed to survive,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357488
    m_Localized: but some very peculiar prohibitions.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357489
    m_Localized: Mentioning outside.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357490
    m_Localized: Exactly. Keeping that in mind,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357491
    m_Localized: have you ever looked into it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357492
    m_Localized: No, I haven't.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357493
    m_Localized: I see. That is wise.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357494
    m_Localized: Why would you come to a dangerous section on purpose?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357495
    m_Localized: Just a little walk.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357496
    m_Localized: It is dangerous, yes,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357497
    m_Localized: but the paintings show you what that danger is.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357498
    m_Localized: And wondering what painting might come next
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357499
    m_Localized: is rather interesting.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357500
    m_Localized: That sounds morbid to me. Sadistic, even.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357501
    m_Localized: Ahaha! Yes, one could see it that way.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357502
    m_Localized: I used to think so myself.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357503
    m_Localized: But now I have come to enjoy looking at the paintings.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168759357504
    m_Localized: My daughter, you see,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746048
    m_Localized: was like you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746049
    m_Localized: She could never be satisfied with only what was already here.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746050
    m_Localized: And I kept denying that part of her...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746051
    m_Localized: I told her to paint brighter things.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746052
    m_Localized: And that is how she ended up a wanderer.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746053
    m_Localized: She was
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746054
    m_Localized: far more honest than I was.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746055
    m_Localized: I think you are honest too.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746056
    m_Localized: Yes. Perhaps I am.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746057
    m_Localized: Do you regret it?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746058
    m_Localized: I was afraid.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746059
    m_Localized: Of outside?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746060
    m_Localized: Of outside, yes.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746061
    m_Localized: And of my daughter learning things I did not know,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746062
    m_Localized: and even things
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746063
    m_Localized: I did not want her to know.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746064
    m_Localized: But there is a saying, is there not?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746065
    m_Localized: If you love your child, send them out into the world.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746066
    m_Localized: For you, 'the lion throws its cub off a cliff' feels more fitting.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746067
    m_Localized: Why? The meaning is the same, is it not?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746068
    m_Localized: In your case,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746069
    m_Localized: it sounds more like possessiveness and fear turned inside out.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746070
    m_Localized: (...!!)
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746071
    m_Localized: Are you trying to... psychoanalyze me?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746072
    m_Localized: No... that was not really what I meant.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746073
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746074
    m_Localized: I spoke out of turn. I'm sorry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746075
    m_Localized: ...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746076
    m_Localized: No, I was the one who lost his composure.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746077
    m_Localized: I apologize.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746078
    m_Localized: You have not exactly aged gracefully.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746079
    m_Localized: You have a talent for saying things that cut deep.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746080
    m_Localized: But without that much nerve,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746081
    m_Localized: perhaps one cannot crack this world's shell.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746082
    m_Localized: Was that a compliment?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746083
    m_Localized: Half of one.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746084
    m_Localized: Listen carefully, Mr. Mouse.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746085
    m_Localized: There is a place ahead that no one wants to go near.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746086
    m_Localized: Only the path leading there is always quiet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746087
    m_Localized: Do you think there is a clue to outside there?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746088
    m_Localized: I do not know.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746089
    m_Localized: But if this world has something it wants to hide,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746090
    m_Localized: I imagine it would be kept somewhere quiet.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746091
    m_Localized: You know, and perhaps I am not one to talk,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746092
    m_Localized: but do you know how to show any respect to your elders?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746093
    m_Localized: Sorry. I spent my whole life in a cage,
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746094
    m_Localized: so I never really learned how to talk to other people.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 168767746095
    m_Localized: I see. So did I.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
